data.title: Primary health care coverage in Brazil: a dataset from 1998 to 2020
data.meta_description: The dataset gathers official and public information from the "e-Gestor AB" platform of the Ministry of Health of Brazil and restricted data obtained by the Brazilian Access to Information Law.
